{"tid":1249571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【溫故知新】2014年香港警察包圍示威者後逼迫示威者當眾排泄","createTime":"2019-06-21T18:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T18:10:39.000Z","uid":252321,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c3400b669c07f44ad2d14ff98303dd0060726abc","tid":1249571,"uid":252321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S22jWir.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS22jWir.png&h=1b7850e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20140928/52951569\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20140928%2F52951569&d=ow9JOMNIA3MeF92spim0Pm9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=a420bb0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20140928%2F52951569&h=7cb26a5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20140928/52951569</a><br />\n學生及示威者前晚成功重奪公民廣場，卻遭警方重重包圍，甚至慘遭不人道對待，包括拒絕在廣場內的集會人士前往洗手間，要求他們在眾目睽睽下「就地解決」，男子只能用膠樽，女士就要用膠袋並用雨傘遮檔。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/363240187097374/posts/713885668699489/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F363240187097374%2Fposts%2F713885668699489%2F&d=ow9JOMNIA3MeF92spim0Pm9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=80dd1c88\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/363240187097374/posts/713885668699489/</a><br />\n香港警察禁止在公民廣場的示威者上廁所，警察迫示威者就地小便，大便。警察也禁止市民遞塑膠給女示威者，迫女示威者就地解決大便小便。<br />\n<br />\n621事件，一個字：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">報應</span></span><br />\n<br />\n免責聲明：我621全日喱埋喺冷氣房做鍵盤戰士"}]}